title: Free Teamspeak oceteamspeak.com
body:
Free TeamSpeak for OCE ** oceteamspeak.com

Feel free to use this as you wish and please share it around!!!

All users can make temp channels with a password

temp channels can become permanent by msgng GOA Yeahman in teamspeak or on league :D

(Non profit) Just want to give back to OCE

replies.body: There should be a looking to play channel where people can find people to play with or just some people to mess around with.
i did have it but no one ever used it so i got rid of it you can always make a temp channel with no password saying something like LF players :D
